comments.body:
This was fixed as part of the code restructure for EUCA-2348. It should now only log an exception when a delete marker was found but the delete operation itself failed rather than when it couldn't find a delete marker to remove.

It will now look something like, but only when an actual delete marker exists:
Deletion of delete marker failed for: bucket/key
